Tiny House Nation - Season 4, Episode 13




204 Sq. Ft. Mountaineer Dream Home

Luke and Tina are avid mountaineers. They spend a lot of their time rock climbing, ice climbing and extreme backpacking in all kinds of terrain around the world. As you can imagine, they have accumulated a ton of specialty gear for their outdoorsy hobbies. Now these two engineers have brought John and Zack in to help build them the wood cabin tiny house of their dreams, and figure out exactly how they're going to store all their gear!




Original Air Date: 25-Jun-2016
